data.text:
Welcome to the website of Chhatna Chandidas Mahavidyalaya

Our college believes in holistic education rather than simply syllabus-oriented-study and students are provided with opportunity to join NSS Training and study tour etc.The Teachers, Teaching Supporting Staffs, Students, Parents, Alumni along with, Principal convey thanks to you for visiting the website.

Malavika Sinha

Principal
